citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 14:15-14:45
on 14-Mar-18.
Arrived at facility to find no one at home. Knocked on door and honked horn. Called listed phone number but
received no answer.
